title: 24. Hashtag Fail
itunes:title: 24. Hashtag Fail
description: Failure is guaranteed. Most people fear failure so much, that they don't even begin what they want to do. They make excuse after excuse and never make any progress. In today's episode, I share with you the 4 steps you must know in order to understand failure, and how to utilize it, so that you can build yourself up into an unstoppable force that can accomplish anything.
